        <div class="application-image thumbnail"  data-dest="https://sourceforge.net/software/link?oaparams=2__bannerid=27446__zoneid=24813__cb=ea44f6d12f__oadest=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.runn.io%2F%3Futm_source%3Dsourceforge%26utm_medium%3Dpaid-review%26utm_campaign%3Dreview-portals" data-newtab="true" data-target="_blank" rel="nofollow">
            <img class="main-image" src="//a.fsdn.com/con/app/nel_img/5194" alt="Runn is a modern resource and capacity planning platform that gets remote teams on the same page. Icon">
            
        </div>
        <div class="wrapper">
            <div class="heading">
                <div class="heading-main">
                    
                    <span data-dest="https://sourceforge.net/software/link?oaparams=2__bannerid=27446__zoneid=24813__cb=ea44f6d12f__oadest=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.runn.io%2F%3Futm_source%3Dsourceforge%26utm_medium%3Dpaid-review%26utm_campaign%3Dreview-portals" data-newtab="true" data-target="_blank" rel="nofollow" title="Find out more about Runn is a modern resource and capacity planning platform that gets remote teams on the same page.">Runn is a modern resource and capacity planning platform that gets remote teams on the same page.</span>

                    
                    <p class="teaser">Runn is best suited for project managers, operations leads, resourcing managers and other people responsible for project delivery.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            
            

            <div class="tiles">
                <div class="tile">
                    
                    <div class="description ">
                        <div class="description-inner">
                            Runn has a modern and easy-to-use interface that provides your team with a shared view of all the people and projects in your organization. Plan new work alongside existing projects and instantly see how changes to your plans and resourcing affect your company’s bottom line.

Runn is intuitive to use and lets you quickly schedule work using simple drag and drop functionality. Runn also allows you to collaborate with your co-workers in real-time, seeing updates live without having to refresh your browser.

Runn combines resource and capacity planning with integrated actual tracking and powerful forecasting to deliver meaningful insights and a full picture of your organization.
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                
            </div>

        </div>

        
